== 根据查询更新
[source]
----
POST {index}/_update_by_query
{
  "script": {
    "source": "ctx._source['field_name'] = 'field_value'",
    "lang": "painless"
  },
  "query": {
    "term": {
      "field_name": "field_value"
    }
  }
}
----

